1
00:00:09,940 --> 00:00:11,080
Embezzling company funds

2
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:13,050
to lavish on a gigolo.

3
00:00:13,050 --> 00:00:14,050
How pathetic.

4
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:15,350
Hey.

5
00:00:15,350 --> 00:00:16,550
What do you think you're doing?

6
00:00:16,720 --> 00:00:18,080
What's the meaning of this?

7
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:20,150
How dare you treat my wife that way.

8
00:00:20,150 --> 00:00:22,220
No, it's not like that...

9
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:24,560
Could you please stop with the

10
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:26,290
pathetic excuses?

11
00:00:26,860 --> 00:00:27,860
Don't you care?

12
00:00:28,190 --> 00:00:28,960
Your company is about to sign

13
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:30,160
a major contract with us.

14
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,560
That won't be an issue.

15
00:00:32,230 --> 00:00:33,000
Just a moment ago,

16
00:00:33,230 --> 00:00:34,930
your company

17
00:00:34,930 --> 00:00:36,470
passed a resolution for your dismissal.

18
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:38,410
Why?

19
00:00:40,410 --> 00:00:41,270
President Kurogane adores me.

20
00:00:41,310 --> 00:00:42,710
All I have to do is say the word,

21
00:00:43,140 --> 00:00:44,880
and getting someone like you fired

22
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,350
is a piece of cake.

23
00:00:48,850 --> 00:00:50,280
For the disrespect you've shown my wife,

24
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:52,150
I expect an immediate
apology.

25
00:00:58,060 --> 00:01:00,160
That incident with the bug in the food,
I'm almost certain it was

26
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:01,160
orchestrated by my husband
and Reika-san.

27
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:03,260
That woman has outlived
her usefulness.

28
00:01:03,260 --> 00:01:04,260
So they figured

29
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:05,570
it was time to cast her aside.

30
00:01:06,130 --> 00:01:07,330
That's certainly the kind of cold,

31
00:01:07,330 --> 00:01:08,900
calculated decision Reika-san would make.

32
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:10,970
But this video...

33
00:01:11,300 --> 00:01:11,970
No, that's not it.

34
00:01:12,270 --> 00:01:13,140
The person who sent that video around...

35
00:01:13,140 --> 00:01:14,210
It's so obvious.

36
00:01:14,810 --> 00:01:15,810
It had to be him.

37
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,040
He's one of them.

38
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:18,110
So is he.

39
00:01:18,110 --> 00:01:19,110
And him too.

40
00:01:19,610 --> 00:01:20,780
They must be

41
00:01:20,950 --> 00:01:23,520
the people my father planted
to keep an eye on me.

42
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:25,150
My father...

43
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:27,290
is the president of Kurogane Holdings.
